statements: SELECT * FROM ImpactAssessment;
SELECT commercial_development, assessment_date FROM ImpactAssessment;
SELECT assessment_id, impact_on_small_businesses FROM ImpactAssessment WHERE assessment_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM ImpactAssessment WHERE commercial_development = 'New Construction';
SELECT impact_on_small_businesses, commercial_development FROM ImpactAssessment WHERE assessment_id = 10;
SELECT * FROM ImpactAssessment ORDER BY assessment_id DESC;
SELECT commercial_development, assessment_date FROM ImpactAssessment WHERE impact_on_small_businesses='High';
SELECT assessment_date, commercial_development, impact_on_small_businesses FROM ImpactAssessment WHERE assessment_date < '2022-01-01' ORDER BY assessment_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM ImpactAssessment WHERE commercial_development LIKE '%software%' AND impact_on_small_businesses IS NOT NULL;
SELECT MAX(assessment_id) AS max_id, MIN(assessment_id) AS min_id FROM ImpactAssessment;
SELECT * FROM SmallBusinesses;
SELECT business_id, business_name FROM SmallBusinesses WHERE business_type = 'Retail';
SELECT development_name, development_location FROM CommercialDevelopments WHERE development_type = 'Office Building';
SELECT business_id, business_name, business_location FROM SmallBusinesses WHERE business_location = 'New York';
SELECT * FROM SmallBusinesses WHERE business_type = 'Restaurant' ORDER BY business_name DESC;
SELECT business_id, business_name, business_type, business_location FROM SmallBusinesses WHERE business_type = 'Retail';
SELECT * FROM SmallBusinesses ORDER BY business_name DESC;
SELECT development_name, development_location FROM CommercialDevelopments WHERE development_type = 'Industrial' AND development_location = 'Denver';
SELECT business_name, business_location FROM SmallBusinesses WHERE business_location LIKE '%York%';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_businesses FROM SmallBusinesses;
SELECT * FROM new_commercial_developments;
SELECT development_name, development_address FROM new_commercial_developments WHERE development_type='Residential';
SELECT development_name, development_size FROM new_commercial_developments WHERE development_size > 1000;
SELECT * FROM small_businesses ORDER BY business_revenue DESC;
SELECT business_name, business_owner, business_address FROM small_businesses WHERE business_type='Retail'
SELECT * FROM new_commercial_developments WHERE development_size > 1000 ORDER BY development_name DESC;
SELECT development_name, development_address FROM new_commercial_developments WHERE development_type = 'Retail' AND development_size BETWEEN 500 AND 1500;
SELECT b.business_name, b.business_owner, ia.impact_score FROM small_businesses b JOIN impact_assessment ia ON b.business_id = ia.business_id WHERE ia.assessment_date = '2022-01-15';

SELECT development_name, development_address, impact_score FROM new_commercial_developments d JOIN impact_assessment ia ON d.development_id = ia.development_id WHERE ia.impact_score > 70 ORDER BY ia.impact_score DESC;

SELECT d.development_name, b.business_name, ia.impact_score FROM new_commercial_developments d JOIN impact_assessment ia ON d.development_id = ia.development_id JOIN small_businesses b ON ia.business_id = b.business_id WHERE d.development_type = 'Office' AND ia.impact_score >= 50 ORDER BY d.development_name ASC, b.business_name ASC;
SELECT business_owner_id, business_name, business_type, business_location FROM BusinessOwners;
SELECT * FROM CommercialDevelopments WHERE development_type = 'Retail';
SELECT development_name, estimated_impact FROM CommercialDevelopments ORDER BY estimated_impact DESC;
SELECT * FROM ImpactAssessment WHERE assessment_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_businesses FROM SmallBusinesses WHERE business_size = 'Small';
SELECT * FROM BusinessOwners WHERE business_type = 'Retail';
SELECT business_name, business_location FROM BusinessOwners WHERE business_location = 'City Center' ORDER BY business_name ASC;
SELECT development_name, development_location, estimated_impact FROM CommercialDevelopments WHERE estimated_impact > 500 ORDER BY estimated_impact DESC;
SELECT assessment_id, assessment_date, assessment_result FROM ImpactAssessment WHERE assessment_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY assessment_date ASC;
SELECT business_name, business_location, business_size FROM SmallBusinesses WHERE business_size IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM SmallBusinesses;
SELECT business_name, business_location FROM SmallBusinesses WHERE revenue > 100000;
SELECT development_name, construction_cost FROM CommercialDevelopments ORDER BY construction_cost DESC;
SELECT assessment_score, assessment_date FROM ImpactAssessment WHERE assessment_score > 5 AND assessment_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT business_name, impact_category FROM AssessmentResults INNER JOIN SmallBusinesses ON AssessmentResults.assessment_id = SmallBusinesses.business_id WHERE impact_category = 'High';
SELECT * FROM SmallBusinesses WHERE revenue > 10000;
SELECT business_name, revenue FROM SmallBusinesses ORDER BY revenue DESC;
SELECT * FROM CompetitionAnalysis WHERE impact_score >= 8 ORDER BY analysis_date DESC;
SELECT SmallBusinesses.business_id, CommercialDevelopments.development_name FROM SmallBusinesses JOIN CommercialDevelopments ON SmallBusinesses.business_id = CommercialDevelopments.development_id;
SELECT business_name, assessment_score, impact_category FROM SmallBusinesses JOIN AssessmentResults ON SmallBusinesses.business_id = AssessmentResults.assessment_id;
